-- Everest Re Group Signs NonBinding Deal to Acquire Heartland Crop Insurance
-- B y   A n d r e w   F r y e
-- 2010-12-15T13:46:08Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-15/everest-re-group-says-it-may-acquire-heartland-crop-insurance.html
Everest Re Group Ltd. , the Bermuda-
based insurer and reinsurer, said it signed a non-binding letter
of intent to acquire Heartland Crop Insurance Inc.  “The potential transaction remains subject to negotiation
and execution of definitive agreements, and there can be no
assurance that a definitive agreement will be entered into or
that the discussions will result in a transaction,” Everest Re
said today in a Business Wire statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
 Andrew Frye  in New York at 
 afrye@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dan Kraut at   dkraut2@bloomberg.net . 